time complexity: O(n log k)
space complexity: O(n)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: This solution uses a priority queue to store the words and their frequencies. The priority queue is ordered by frequency in descending order, and then by lexicographical order. The top k elements are then popped from the priority queue and added to the result vector.

